@node inst "How do I... Install : 1° type 'WIN.exe' next to the DOS PROMPT 'C:\>'..."
@font digitalQuill.font 11

===============================================================================
USE                             in order to                     And you'll get
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
SWAZINFO                        replace your old icons          my icons !
Screenmode in prefs drawer      reach 32 colors                 a 32 colors WB
Fullpalette                     load in my 32 colz palette      the right colors
================================================================================

And please delete all the old fonts distributed by me (BNS, MACicon, MACtitle...) and have a look in the FONTS drawer of this pack, everything have been reworked (kerns and spaces have changed to a more compact way).
